4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/5389-0
00:37:49.985 --> 00:37:51.215
<v Siim Vene>Siis selline nagu.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/5391-0
