01:13:29.505 --> 01:13:33.575
<v Lars Asi>See on lihtsalt haldab kontrollimise.
Sinu jaoks on naudid nüüd tead,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10141-1
01:13:33.575 --> 01:13:38.228
<v Lars Asi>nüüd on teinud selle veel lihtsamaks,
et panid sellise asja nagu auto mod et sa</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10141-2
01:13:38.228 --> 01:13:39.915
<v Lars Asi>ei pea enam nõuda ka haldama.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10164-0
01:13:40.955 --> 01:13:45.330
<v Lars Asi>Ee aga see muutub väga ohtlikuks,
kui keegi arendajatest ütleb,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10164-1
01:13:45.330 --> 01:13:49.295
<v Lars Asi>et tal on vaja nüüd 10 kooris chipitud ja
100 giga rammi.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10209-0
01:13:50.505 --> 01:13:54.877
<v Lars Asi>Vt hea meelega annab selle,
neil on ka rasked ajad finantsiliselt,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10209-1
01:13:54.877 --> 01:13:59.773
<v Lars Asi>nii et piirangud ja turvameetmed tuleb
nende mänge teenustega peale panna,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10209-2
01:13:59.773 --> 01:14:03.623
<v Lars Asi>sest seal on väga kerge,
väga palju raha väga kiiresti ära</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10209-3
01:14:03.623 --> 01:14:05.125
<v Lars Asi>kulutada, eriti praegu.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10218-0
01:14:04.345 --> 01:14:08.815
<v Siim Vene>No kuule accessil on ikkagi on ju
kasumimarginaal on ju nelikümmend 4%.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10254-0
01:14:09.365 --> 01:14:14.163
<v Lars Asi>Jah, sest praegu ma olen lugenud ka,
et ee SO inimestel tekib probleem ei</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10254-1
01:14:14.163 --> 01:14:17.664
<v Lars Asi>mudelitega,
sest need skreipi vad nende lehekülgi nii</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10254-2
01:14:17.664 --> 01:14:21.619
<v Lars Asi>intensiivselt ja seega neil ongi server
les siis server las.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10254-3
01:14:21.619 --> 01:14:23.435
<v Lars Asi>Kohe vastab sinu nõudlusele.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10262-0
01:14:24.175 --> 01:14:27.305
<v Lars Asi>Ja noh arvega kasvab kohe siis.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10325-0
01:14:29.245 --> 01:14:33.807
<v Siim Vene>Nii on jah, et et aga jah,
mulle see matsi matsi reflektsioon</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10325-1
01:14:33.807 --> 01:14:38.811
<v Siim Vene>meeldib, et peamine eristus on see,
et üks on päris kuberner ütles,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10325-2
01:14:38.811 --> 01:14:42.711
<v Siim Vene>et eks ta enam vähem nii kipubki olema.
Jah, et noh,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10289-0
01:14:40.555 --> 01:14:40.985
<v Lars Asi>Noh.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10325-3
01:14:42.711 --> 01:14:48.083
<v Siim Vene>kummaline on lihtsalt minu jaoks.
Seega et etno, et sellesama 1. eksole,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10325-4
01:14:48.083 --> 01:14:50.365
<v Siim Vene>nagu sa ütlesid ka, et et nagu.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10366-0
01:14:51.585 --> 01:14:53.990
<v Siim Vene>Et kui sul on nagu nii öelda see kuber
näites,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10366-1
01:14:53.990 --> 01:14:57.164
<v Siim Vene>mis on mõnes mõttes nagu tööstuse
standardiks juba kujunenud,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10366-2
01:14:57.164 --> 01:15:00.645
<v Siim Vene>et miks sa pead seda terminoloogiat
hakkama? 0 jalgratast leiutama,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10366-3
01:15:00.645 --> 01:15:03.512
<v Siim Vene>miks sa ei või samu termineid kasutada?
Näiteks eksole,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10356-0
01:15:02.435 --> 01:15:02.945
<v Lars Asi>Mhmh.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10366-4
01:15:03.512 --> 01:15:06.635
<v Siim Vene>et ei igaüks peab ikka ise midagi tegema.
Eks ole tingimata.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10402-0
01:15:08.685 --> 01:15:10.742
<v Siim Vene>Vot kuule,
aga see oli praegu väga sujuv</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10402-1
01:15:10.742 --> 01:15:13.853
<v Siim Vene>sissejuhatus labori poole peale,
et kuidas me teeme. Arvasin,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10402-2
01:15:13.853 --> 01:15:17.365
<v Siim Vene>et ma panen praegu salvestuse seisma
seisma. Siis paneb uuesti käima,</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10402-3
01:15:17.365 --> 01:15:20.175
<v Siim Vene>et siis tekib nii öelda labori jaoks
eraldi salvestuse.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10412-0
01:15:20.555 --> 01:15:22.935
<v Lars Asi>Jah ja ma olen.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10434-0
01:15:21.605 --> 01:15:24.642
<v Siim Vene>Kui aga aga nii teemegi,
et siis ma panen ise käima panen ise</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10419-0
01:15:23.625 --> 01:15:24.045
<v Lars Asi>Jah.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10434-1
01:15:24.642 --> 01:15:28.415
<v Siim Vene>panen ise seisma panen ise käima uuesti,
et sa ei pea tegelema selleks siis.</v>

4b4cc10f-3744-4a12-a13e-5539b7e9c80f/10437-0
01:15:28.855 --> 01:15:29.745
<v Lars Asi>Okei aitäh.</v>